' =========================================================
' ネイティブアプリ(Kotlin + Jetpack Compose)アーキテクチャ
' =========================================================
' レイヤー構造は Android 公式「推奨アーキテクチャ」に準拠
'   https://developer.android.com/topic/architecture?hl=ja
'   UI Layer / Domain Layer(Optional) / Data Layer
'   単方向データフロー(UDF)+ Single Source of Truth(SSOT)
' =========================================================
' 収録ダイアグラム:
'   1. native_layer_structure       レイヤ構造(UI / Domain / Data)
'   2. native_udf                   単方向データフロー(UDF)
'   3. native_request_flow          リクエストフロー(カメラアクセス)
'   4. native_ht_scanner            HT バーコードスキャナ連携
'   5. native_hw_capability         HW 機能対応(全て ◎)
'   6. native_update_distribution   更新・配信フロー
'   7. native_jetpack_stack         Jetpack コンポーネント構成
' =========================================================

@startuml 1_native_layer_structure

title 【① 純ネイティブ(Kotlin + Jetpack Compose)】\nレイヤ構造(Android 推奨アーキテクチャ準拠)

skinparam defaultFontName "Meiryo"
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor<<ui>> #C8E6C9
  BackgroundColor<<domain>> #DCEDC8
  BackgroundColor<<data>> #E6EE9C
  BackgroundColor<<external>> #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #2E7D32
}
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor #666
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #FFFDE7
  BorderColor #666
}
skinparam cloud {
  BackgroundColor #ECEFF1
  BorderColor #666
}

package "UI Layer" as UI <<ui>> {
  component "UI Elements\n(Jetpack Compose Composables)\n- `@Composable` 関数\n- Material 3\n- Adaptive Layout" as UI_ELEMENTS
  component "State Holders\n(ViewModel)\n- UI State(StateFlow)\n- イベントハンドラ\n- ビジネスロジックの呼出" as UI_STATE
  UI_ELEMENTS -down-> UI_STATE : observes state\nsends events
}

package "Domain Layer (Optional)" as DOMAIN <<domain>> {
  component "UseCases / Interactors\n- `GetBarcodeHistoryUseCase`\n- `SubmitTransactionUseCase`\n- 再利用可能な業務ロジック" as USECASE
}

package "Data Layer" as DATA <<data>> {
  component "Repositories\n- `BarcodeRepository`\n- `TransactionRepository`\n- SSOT の統合窓口\n- 複数 DataSource の競合解決" as REPO

  package "Data Sources" as DS {
    component "Remote DataSource\n(Retrofit + OkHttp / Ktor)" as DS_REMOTE
    component "Local DataSource\n(Room DAO)" as DS_LOCAL
    component "Preferences DataSource\n(DataStore)" as DS_PREFS
    component "Scanner DataSource\n(DataWedge BroadcastReceiver)" as DS_SCANNER
    component "Sensor DataSource\n(CameraX / Bluetooth / NFC 等)" as DS_SENSOR
  }

  REPO -down-> DS_REMOTE
  REPO -down-> DS_LOCAL
  REPO -down-> DS_PREFS
  REPO -down-> DS_SCANNER
  REPO -down-> DS_SENSOR
}

package "External" as EXT <<external>> {
  cloud "API Server\n(REST / gRPC / WebSocket)" as API
  database "SQLite(Room)\nEncrypted Shared Prefs\nDataStore ファイル" as DB
  component "Android SDK(OS)\nCameraX / BT / BLE / NFC / USB /\nIR / UART / UWB / RFID SDK /\nKeystore / Biometric / WorkManager" as SDK
}

UI_STATE -down-> USECASE : calls
USECASE -down-> REPO : uses

DS_REMOTE -down-> API : HTTPS
DS_LOCAL -down-> DB
DS_PREFS -down-> DB
DS_SCANNER -down-> SDK : Intent Broadcast\nBroadcastReceiver
DS_SENSOR -down-> SDK

note right of UI
  **UI Layer**
  Composable 関数で宣言的に UI を記述
  ViewModel が UI State を StateFlow で公開
  UI Elements は State を観測して再レンダリング
end note

note right of DOMAIN
  **Domain Layer(オプション)**
  複雑な業務ロジックや
  複数 ViewModel で再利用するロジックを切り出す
  小規模なら省略可
end note

note right of DATA
  **Data Layer**
  Repository が SSOT として振る舞い
  DataSource の詳細を上位から隠蔽
  オフラインファーストなら Local DB を SSOT に
end note

note bottom of EXT
  ネイティブ App は Android SDK の **全 API** に
  直接アクセス可能。ブリッジ層・プラグイン層なし
end note

@enduml

' =========================================================

@startuml 2_native_udf

title 【② ネイティブ】 単方向データフロー(UDF)+ SSOT

skinparam defaultFontName "Meiryo"

actor User

package "UI Layer" as UI {
  component "Composable\n(UI Elements)" as COMP
  component "ViewModel\n(StateFlow<UiState>)" as VM
}

package "Domain Layer" as DOMAIN {
  component "UseCase" as UC
}

package "Data Layer" as DATA {
  component "Repository" as REPO
  database "Local DB\n(SSOT)" as DB
  cloud "Remote API" as API
}

User --> COMP : 操作(event)
COMP --> VM : event 通知(onClick 等)
VM --> UC : invoke()
UC --> REPO : fetch / update
REPO --> DB : 優先: Local を返す
REPO --> API : バックグラウンドで同期
API -[#blue]-> DB : 非同期で書込
DB -[#green]-> REPO : Flow で変更通知
REPO -[#green]-> UC : Flow
UC -[#green]-> VM : Flow
VM -[#green]-> COMP : StateFlow 変更通知
COMP -[#green]-> User : 画面再描画

note right of DB
  **SSOT(Single Source of Truth)**
  Local DB が唯一の信頼できる情報源
  オフライン時も安定動作
end note

note left of VM
  **StateFlow** で
  UI State を immutable に公開
  UI はこれを collect する
end note

legend right
  | 方向 | 意味 |
  |<color:black>━━━▶</color>| イベント(User → 下方) |
  |<color:green>━━━▶</color>| State(Data → UI 方向) |
  |<color:blue>━━━▶</color>| 非同期同期 |
endlegend

@enduml

